modName: Alicia And Janelle Followers CBBE And UUNP Full HDT
summary: Adds 2 lovely followers to the game.
descriptionHtml:
Kind of like the Frito Lay commercial in which the catchphrase is "can't stop at one". Both ladies are focused on mainly melee and ranged combat with the exception of Alicia who has a firebolt spell. Janelle is an Elf Vampire and is ready for bloodthirst mod or vampire mods. She also uses a healing staff to heal her, you and your other followers. The heal staff can be taken from her inventory and used by the player also. Alicia is just a Nord. They both have tweaked health, magicka, and stamina and speed. Both are essential and marriageable and are recommended for higher levels. They can be found inside the front entrance of Cragslane Cavern (coc cragslanecavern01). If you have xp32 and hdt installed you will get full body bounce animations in both cbbe and uunp. The bikinis were from this mod. https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/11764
Note: Remember if you use AFT or UFO to place them below my follower mod after installing so they work. Also, please use the bug report section for submitting bugs and not the forums so I can better assist and keep the forums from getting cluttered. Other than that enjoy!
author: Sapphire
